Changes:


In-progress - Interim developer release 0.2 (aim for 11/1/08):

* Add full_{x,y,z} fields to ImageSpec, to allow full expression of
  OpenEXR's 'dataWindow'.
* iv now properly handles display/full windows.
* Change some API signatures from char* to std::string.
* Move texture functionality inside libimageio.so.
* Change plugin 'imageio_version' symbol to '<FORMAT>_imageio_version' so
  that multiple formats can be in a DSO without name clashes.
* 'make EMBEDPLUGINS=1' will include the built-in format plugins into
  libimageio.so itself, and not dist the separate plugin DSO's.


Initial developer release 0.1 (9/1/08):

* ImageInput, ImageOutput, TextureSystem APIs pretty mature
* Plugins: TIFF, JPEG/JFIF, OpenEXR, PNG, HDR/rgbe
* iv - basic display, multiple images, menus, status bar, info window,
  basic prefs window, pixel view tool, zoom, pan, open, open recent,
  close, save as, view subimages, view channels, gamma, exposure,
  fit window to image, fit image to window, full screen.
* iconvert
* idiff
* maketx
* API docs for ImageInput, ImageOutput, writing plugins
* Linux and OSX


